{"tid":2447961,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Rosé「歷代最貴專輯」惹議 韓網友：這不是K-pop","createTime":"2021-03-15T14:31:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T02:38:00.000Z","uid":231132,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"70151c5b67d6fefa560c02fd5d013a67b33dc851","tid":2447961,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T14:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KLnCD6J.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKLnCD6J.jpg&h=80e650cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBLACKPINK成員Ros&eacute;日前成功SOLO出道，粉絲等候多時終於盼來這張「歷代最貴」專輯，其中收錄的歌曲《GONE》在演唱會搶先表演時，就得到了極好的反應，不過主打歌《On The Ground》釋出後，卻有南韓網友相當不解為何收錄的兩首都是全英文歌曲，因此在網路上引起一片討論。<br />\n<br />\nRos&eacute; SOLO專輯的主打歌《On The Ground》一釋出就取得相當好的成績，MV從12日發布至今已有近7000萬的觀看人次，她在打歌節目上穩健的臺風與優異的唱歌實力也讓粉絲相當佩服，不過近日南韓網友對於專輯收錄了兩首英文歌曲感到失望，認為Ros&eacute;只考慮到國際聽眾，沒有顧及到韓國的聽眾。<br />\n<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n有網友看到文章後表示同意並直呼：「這樣就不是K-pop了。」不過也有粉絲出面緩頰表示自己能夠理解，因為英文原本就是她熟悉的語言，只要本人覺得合適就好，況且Ros&eacute;的海外粉絲人數較多，發行英語歌曲對於她進入歐美市場更有利。"},{"pid":"d88f3cb56003f57a40bea0fa849a5acc31c8ac9d","tid":2447961,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"此留言區已被關閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88b55e557d3e7c2b5977663e1dc14bd1f3c3011","tid":2447961,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d88f3cb56003f57a40bea0fa849a5acc31c8ac9d","tid":2447961,"uid":165368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T15:23:49.000Z","msg":"此留言區已被關閉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:05:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1837a52a041ae131b76f69105f30f70494664d73","tid":2447961,"uid":60145,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"好難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54f85d3f0ed8fa069c874bd2068396f56136672","tid":2447961,"uid":274500,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T01:32:56.000Z","msg":"班人煩到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 出英文歌都要嘈"},{"pid":"955061e033def5a8f633e959d1bd354a1dd81d69","tid":2447961,"uid":167658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:27:24.000Z","msg":"Gone好聽過On the Ground"},{"pid":"4a4bb693d3ec06d82435da5174cf673431c043d8","tid":2447961,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"BLACKPINK=FRAUD"}]}